{"tid":1631561,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"自問好好打嘅同我入哂黎","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T03:27:02.000Z","uid":266935,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"52272bae0cec5d54ea533296aa164fa64231a398","tid":1631561,"uid":266935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:59.000Z","msg":"首先，我為之前堅持集中一區道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因為真係難以想像黨鐵做到咁卑賤，做到變「 EmptyR」，令所有人得返巴士呢個選項，結果班狗完場拉人嘅難度降低...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好，講返正題，今日出去發完夢，我有兩個戰術推介。<br />\n<br />\n一，係泥魔法。利申，我對鞋今日係暴雨之下食哂泥魔法，抹到我傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係大家發夢掘磚嘅同時，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我發現大家忽略左磚低下/樹低嘅泥都可以好有用</span></span>，食中濕左嘅泥不單視線會受阻，更加會覺得好污糟要抹走佢。之前有人講過要扔顏色彈/雞蛋，但啲狗依家帶乜都拉，所以更加要利用身邊見到嘅素材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你可能會問，下星期無雨落咁點算，come on HKers，水呢家野前線要個陣，一車車運上去都得喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事後巴我係goal-oriented嘅人，用泥魔法有以下嘅目的：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 影響中泥者視線<br />\n2. 令中泥者難以清洗乾淨<br />\n3. 令香港嘅大自然出一份力 The nature will rise against you </span></span><br />\n不過我唔係化學巴，跪求化學巴指教可唔可以加啲物質入泥度，令泥魔法威力更大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二，係鶳戰術。經常有坊間市民及國際媒體表示鶳好暴力好唔文明。的確，見紅係麻煩啲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />既然係咁，唔見紅咪得囉你班豬仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以點做呀即係，我強調我絕不建議向全港唯一攞左牌嘅電視台學野，因為呢一招打天下，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">名為「帶馬歸槽」</span></span>，無錯，係要跟King Sir同馬明學野，詳情請參閱<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U3XOCPfzlYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DU3XOCPfzlYA&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL2o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=751241c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U3XOCPfzlYA</a> (0:50-0:56)<br />\n或者你覺得呢招好白痴，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但重點係取其精神，即係打關節呀拗斷人手手腳腳咁</span></span>，咁賤嘅野野我就跟黑警學嘅，但未夠十八歲嘅唔好學呀!!PG家長指引!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同樣地，事後巴重申自己係goal-oriented嘅人，用「帶馬歸槽」嘅目的係：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 中招者頓時失去反抗能力(唔信你叫你隔離個個試下拗你關節，我以前食夜粥個時有痛苦經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n2. 唔見血好睇好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 中招者輕則一個月內無法使用手/腳; 重則...你問黑警喇<br />\n4. 阻嚇所有藍絲廢老，甚至狗隻唔好輕易撩交打，後果自負<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後三句，第一句係大家千萬唔好做暴力行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第二句係求問有無畢業公仔公司/舖頭有得平整連尼豬公仔，我好想要亦好想得到連登版權同意...第三句係拋磚引玉，希望高人繼續指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871eda85574f1b5ea98fe750edc801b013782056","tid":1631561,"uid":266935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:48:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be74c86be47701414175ebfbaafd307b9bfa739c","tid":1631561,"uid":266935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:48:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1edf20bb4fb96967503538c574c5151538149f4","tid":1631561,"uid":266935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:48:57.000Z","msg":"有用架我諗，推"},{"pid":"3d8c2fa84a9c78fa63ab81aac1651e64a407f5f0","tid":1631561,"uid":266935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:49:11.000Z","msg":"推爆"},{"pid":"c4f393fb323385b0d26c646e639e916d9e9eb9f2","tid":1631561,"uid":262301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:49:18.000Z","msg":"可唔可以應承我<br />\n以後凡係有落單狗 / 先撩者賤嘅藍絲， 一撚定要扑斷四隻手腳<br />\n仲要係粉碎性骨折果種<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係粉碎性骨折！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b030563f8297f013fc034fcb1b20451d0fe9d3f3","tid":1631561,"uid":266935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:49:21.000Z","msg":"爆推"},{"pid":"35156557acdf48b2885c6b03a09473c45831e6d3","tid":1631561,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:49:51.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n記唔記得當初應承過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈都唔割</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣洗地</span></strong></span>開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"85ac331f3cc08a39e17f0f28f667a6c9e9862da3","tid":1631561,"uid":266935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4f393fb323385b0d26c646e639e916d9e9eb9f2","tid":1631561,"uid":262301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:49:18.000Z","msg":"可唔可以應承我<br />\n以後凡係有落單狗 / 先撩者賤嘅藍絲， 一撚定要扑斷四隻手腳<br />\n仲要係粉碎性骨折果種<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係粉碎性骨折！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:31.00